        "name": "Virtuoso",
        "description": "<p>You can use your Action or skip your Move to make a Performance Check. If you pass, your Group gains one of the following benefits of your choice for that Round:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Inspiration:</strong> d6 bonus to Healing rolls</p></li><li><p><strong>Resolve:</strong> Favor on Saves</p></li><li><p><strong>Valor:</strong> Favor on Attack and Cast Checks</p></li></ul>",
